        {
            "title": "摩根大通預期宏觀基金回歸將推動股市上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkT.J6EQ.Cm0QnT5ytAxjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7306L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根大通\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根大通;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根大通\">摩根大通</a>預測,隨著宏觀<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"對沖基金\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:對沖基金;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/對沖基金\">對沖基金</a>在3月份大幅回調後被迫重建其股票敞口,股市將在短期內獲得提振,其中美國大型科技股被視為最大的潛在受益者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Nikolaos Panigirtzoglou在給客戶的報告中寫道,宏觀對沖基金的股票貝塔值在3月份大幅下降,使得該類基金在4月份的反彈中處於不利位置。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因此,摩根大通認為這些基金面臨重返市場的壓力。Panigirtzoglou寫道:\"宏觀對沖基金可能會在未來幾週內被迫重建其股票敞口,從而推動股市上漲,特別是如果當前的停火協議能夠促成伊朗與美國之間更持久的協議。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3804c09b-78d5-3945-a720-e6e688fe844d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在股票方面,摩根大通強調QQQ ETF的高做淡倉位是額外上漲空間的來源。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示:\"QQQ ETF較高的做淡倉位意味著有更大的空頭回補空間,因此美國大型科技股有更大的上漲潛力。\"該公司指出,科技股和通訊股在3月和4月初遭遇大量資金流出,而同期只有能源、工業和公用事業板塊出現資金流入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場結構方面,摩根大通指出,美國、歐洲和日本股市的流動性已惡化至解放日以來的最低水平,而布蘭特原油和WTI期貨的流動性已跌至2022年以來的低點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金期貨的流動性自1月下旬拋售以來一直受損,目前已跌至疫情以來的最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對沖基金整體在3月份虧損約2.5%,抹去了1月和2月的大部分漲幅,事件驅動型基金和股票多空基金在第一季度結束時處於負值區域。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-133614899.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 21:56:23",
